Text: What's the quality of the cam like,...?

Bit dark in places but not bad for a cam. Watchable. 6/10. The sync goes out in the second half of the film a little bit but if you really want to watch it and can't wait for a better copy then this should do! This guy is normally pretty reliable, i've downloaded many of his uploads in the past and they're always pretty good.  Thanks for the upload MQFPLO.
